oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bob Wills Live at the Ozark Jubilee - 1957-03-30 - Reel 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Bob Wills (musician) live at the Ozark Jubilee. The performance is accompanied by Texas Playboys. The show is hosted by Red Foley. The recording is from March 30, 1957. The tape is labeled reel one.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Bob Wills
